Block_Criteria.Criteria: asg.legislation_code='US' AND asg.assignment_type='E' --AND asg.person_id in ('300000039451955','300000036828315') AND EXISTS ( SELECT paaf1.Assignment_id FROM per_all_assignments_f paaf1, pay_payroll_assignments ppa1, pay_pay_relationships_dn pprd1, (SELECT papd.payroll_term_id,papd.payroll_id FROM pay_assigned_payrolls_dn papd) papd WHERE paaf1.assignment_id = ppa1.hr_assignment_id AND papd.payroll_term_id(+) = ppa1.payroll_term_id AND ppa1.payroll_relationship_id = pprd1.payroll_relationship_id AND paaf1.work_terms_assignment_id = ppa1.hr_term_id AND papd.payroll_id IN ( SELECT papf2.PAYROLL_ID FROM PAY_TIME_PERIODS ptp2, pay_all_payrolls_f papf2 WHERE ptp2.PERIOD_NAME = pay_report_utils.get_parameter_value('PAYROLL_RUN_ID') AND ptp2.PAYROLL_ID = papf2.PAYROLL_ID AND ptp2.PERIOD_CATEGORY = 'E' AND TRUNC(SYSDATE) between papf2.EFFECTIVE_START_DATE AND papf2.EFFECTIVE_END_DATE AND papf2.legislative_Data_group_id = (SELECT legislative_Data_group_id FROM PER_LEGISLATIVE_DATA_GROUPS WHERE LEGISLATION_CODE = 'US' )) AND asg.assignment_id = paaf1.Assignment_id ) AND (SELECT ptp11.end_date FROM pay_time_periods ptp11,per_periods_of_service ppos,pay_assigned_payrolls_dn papd12 WHERE ptp11.period_name = pay_report_utils.get_parameter_value('PAYROLL_RUN_ID') AND ptp11.PERIOD_CATEGORY = 'E' AND ptp11.payroll_id = papd12.payroll_id and papd12.payroll_term_id = ppa.payroll_term_id AND papd12.START_DATE = (SELECT max(papd123.START_DATE) FROM pay_assigned_payrolls_dn papd123 WHERE papd123.payroll_term_id = papd12.payroll_term_id AND papd123.START_DATE <=ptp11.end_date) AND ppos.Person_Id = asg.Person_Id AND ppos.period_of_service_id = asg.period_of_service_id AND ppos.date_start=(select max(ppos1.date_start) from per_periods_of_service ppos1 where ppos1.person_id = ppos.person_id AND ppos1.primary_flag='Y' AND ppos1.date_start<=ptp11.end_date) AND ((pay_report_utils.get_parameter_value('INCLUDE_TERMINATED_EMPLOYEES') = 'N' AND ppos.actual_termination_date is NULL) OR (pay_report_utils.get_parameter_value('INCLUDE_TERMINATED_EMPLOYEES') = 'Y' AND (((ppos.actual_termination_date is NULL) OR (ppos.actual_termination_date > SYSDATE)) OR ((ppos.actual_termination_date BETWEEN TRUNC(SYSDATE)-732 AND SYSDATE ) AND asg.action_Code<>'GLB_TRANSFER')))) ) BETWEEN asg.effective_start_date AND asg.effective_end_date AND EXISTS(SELECT 'X' FROM per_seniority_dates_f psd WHERE psd.Person_id = asg.person_id AND psd.seniority_date_code = 'AXE_LIFE_TIME_LOS' AND psd.level_code = 'ORA_P' AND psd.effective_start_date = (select min(psd1.effective_start_date) from per_seniority_dates_f psd1 where psd1.person_id = psd.Person_id and psd1.seniority_date_code = psd.seniority_date_code and psd1.level_code = psd.level_code) ) /*Include AXE Only Employees*/ AND EXISTS ( SELECT 'x' FROM hr_legal_entities hle WHERE hle.organization_id = asg.legal_entity_id AND status = 'A' AND classification_code = 'HCM_LEMP' AND TRUNC(SYSDATE) BETWEEN hle.effective_start_date AND hle.effective_end_date AND hle.organization_code in (SELECT hl.lookup_code FROM hcm_lookups hl WHERE enabled_flag = 'Y' AND lookup_type = 'AXE_HR_ANIXTER_LEGAL_EMP_LKP' ) )

Block_Criteria.Criteria: ppnf.name_type = 'GLOBAL' AND NVL((SELECT distinct ptp.end_Date FROM PER_ALL_PEOPLE_F papf , per_periods_of_service ppos , per_all_assignments_f paaf , pay_payroll_assignments ppa , pay_pay_relationships_dn pprd , pay_time_periods ptp , ( select nvl(( select min(pdf.date_value) from pay_dates pdf , pay_time_definitions ptdf where papd.assigned_payroll_id = pdf.source_id and ptdf.short_name = 'FSED' and pdf.source_type ='AP' and ptdf.time_definition_id =pdf.time_definition_id ) , papd.start_date) as start_date , nvl(( select max(pdf.date_value) from pay_dates pdf , pay_time_definitions ptdf where papd.assigned_payroll_id = pdf.source_id and ptdf.short_name = 'LSED' and pdf.source_type ='AP' and ptdf.time_definition_id =pdf.time_definition_id ) ,papd.end_date) as end_date , papd.payroll_term_id , papd.payroll_id from pay_assigned_payrolls_dn papd ) papd where ppnf.person_id = papf.person_id and ppos.person_id = papf.person_id and ptp.payroll_id = papd.payroll_id and ptp.period_name = pay_report_utils.get_parameter_value('PAYROLL_RUN_ID') AND ptp.PERIOD_CATEGORY = 'E' and paaf.person_id = ppos.person_id and paaf.period_of_service_id = ppos.period_of_service_id and paaf.assignment_id = ppa.hr_assignment_id and papd.payroll_term_id(+) = ppa.payroll_term_id and ppa.payroll_relationship_id = pprd.payroll_relationship_id and paaf.work_terms_assignment_id = ppa.hr_term_id and trunc(ptp.end_date) between papf.effective_start_date and papf.effective_end_date and trunc(ptp.end_date) between paaf.effective_start_date and paaf.effective_end_date and trunc(ptp.end_date) between pprd.start_date and pprd.end_date and trunc(ptp.end_date) between ppa.start_date and ppa.end_date and trunc(ptp.end_date) between papd.start_date(+) and papd.end_date(+) -- and paaf.ASSIGNMENT_TYPE = 'E' AND paaf.EFFECTIVE_LATEST_CHANGE = 'Y' and ppos.date_start = ( SELECT MAX(ppos1.date_start) FROM per_periods_of_service ppos1 WHERE ppos1.person_id = papf.person_id AND ppos1.date_start <= TRUNC(ptp.end_date) ) ),pay_report_utils.get_parameter_value_date('EFFECTIVE_DATE')) BETWEEN ppnf.effective_start_date AND ppnf.effective_end_date

target.INFORMATION_TYPE = ('AXE_US_PENSION_CONTEXT_2')
AND (SELECT ptp15.end_date FROM pay_assigned_payrolls_dn papd16, pay_payroll_assignments ppa16 ,pay_time_periods ptp15 WHERE papd16.payroll_term_id = ppa16.payroll_term_id and ptp15.period_name =pay_report_utils.get_parameter_value('PAYROLL_RUN_ID') AND ptp15.PERIOD_CATEGORY = 'E' and ptp15.payroll_id = papd16.payroll_id AND ppa16.person_id = target.person_id AND ppa16.START_DATE = (SELECT max(ppa164.START_DATE) FROM pay_payroll_assignments ppa164 WHERE ppa164.person_id = ppa16.person_id AND ppa164.START_DATE <=(SELECT max(ppa1.effective_start_date) from per_all_assignments_m ppa1 where ppa1.person_id=target.person_id and ppa1.assignment_type='E' AND ppa1.effective_start_date <= sysdate) ) AND papd16.START_DATE = (SELECT max(papd163.START_DATE) FROM pay_assigned_payrolls_dn papd163 WHERE papd163.payroll_term_id = papd16.payroll_term_id AND papd163.START_DATE <= SYSDATE ) )
BETWEEN target.effective_start_date AND target.effective_end_date

trunc(ptp.end_date) between pprd.start_date and pprd.end_date and trunc(ptp.end_date) between ppa.start_date and ppa.end_date and trunc(ptp.end_date) between papd.start_date(+) and papd.end_date(+) --
